                <h2>Our Ecosystem Focus</h2>
                <p>
                    We actively map and analyze businesses driving impact across three key regional tech corridors:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Hyderabad:</strong> High-growth SaaS pipelines, deep-tech platforms, and premium e-commerce ecosystems.</li>
                    <li><strong>Warangal / Hanamkonda:</strong> Regional tech engines, hyper-local marketplaces, and bootstrap breakthroughs transforming Tier-2 paradigms.</li>
                    <li><strong>Vijayawada:</strong> Fast-scaling consumer brands, agritech solutions, and regional supply chain innovations.</li>
                </ul>
            
                <h2>What We Study</h2>
                <p>
                    Every case study and directory listing on our platform aims to answer the core operational questions: How did they build traction? What is their funding structure? What systems run their backend pipelines? 
                </p>
                <p>By capturing granular detail cards (like revenue models, established milestones, team distribution, and monetization metrics), we serve as an open playbook for local builders.</p>

                <h2>Submit Your Story</h2>
                <p>
